{"tid":206294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：政府擬加急症室收費至180元","createTime":"2017-04-18T09:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T09:49:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"358a66058710bd535477f80881df9c43a2fb10fb","tid":206294,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"消息：政府擬加急症室收費至180元<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】消息透露，政府建議急症室收費由100元加至約180元。<br />\n<br />\n立法會衞生事務委員會下周二討論公立醫院收費檢討。消息指，政府建議將急症室收費由100元調高到大約180元，較醫管局早前委託顧問公司建議加至220元的水平為低。 <br />\n<br />\n有急症專科醫生認為，急症室加費後仍較私家醫生便宜，相信只能略為減輕急症室負荷。公立醫院急症室自2002年底開始，由免費改為收費100元，至今從沒有加價。 <br />\n<br />\n#要聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=218116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D218116&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f7ba5562\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D218116&h=d3067d06\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=218116</a>"},{"pid":"19f2082bb29306e37143fc4e2194fc26bf27338b","tid":206294,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"腦魔啲教友咪又係免費"}]}